.mobile-filter-item-content
    //- a.link.link--black_border(href='#message-you-subscribed' data-popup='{"type":"inline"}') Сообщение об удачной подписке
    a.mobile-filter__link.size-guide-link(href='#message-you-subscribed' data-popup='{"type":"inline"}') Руководство по размерам
    each size in sizes
      .filter-row.filter-row__size
        label.form-checkbox
          input(class='form-item form-item--checkbox' type='checkbox')
          span.form-checkbox-title= size.name
        label.form-checkbox
            input(class='form-item form-item--checkbox' type='checkbox')
            span.form-checkbox-title= size.growth1
        label.form-checkbox
            input(class='form-item form-item--checkbox' type='checkbox')
            span.form-checkbox-title= size.growth2         